🤖 AUTOMATED AI AGENT SYSTEM — CODE GENERATION ENGINE

The AI Agent System (`/js/ai-agent.js`) provides:

### Generate Functions
• `AIAgent.generate.page(options)` — Create full HTML page
• `AIAgent.generate.component(options)` — Create modular component
• `AIAgent.generate.section(options)` — Create page section
• `AIAgent.generate.seoMeta(options)` — Create SEO metadata
• `AIAgent.generate.cssTokens()` — Generate design tokens

### Optimize Functions
• `AIAgent.optimize.html(content)` — Minify HTML
• `AIAgent.optimize.css(content)` — Minify CSS
• `AIAgent.optimize.classNames(element)` — Deduplicate classes

### Validate Functions
• `AIAgent.validate.accessibility(element)` — Check WCAG compliance
• `AIAgent.validate.responsiveness(styles)` — Check breakpoints

### Utility Functions
• `AIAgent.utils.kebabCase(str)` — Convert to kebab-case
• `AIAgent.utils.pascalCase(str)` — Convert to PascalCase
• `AIAgent.utils.generateId()` — Generate unique ID
• `AIAgent.utils.formatDate()` — Format date

### Configuration
• `AIAgent.config.brandColors` — Brand color palette
• `AIAgent.config.fonts` — Typography settings
• `AIAgent.config.breakpoints` — Responsive breakpoints
• `AIAgent.config.spacing` — Spacing tokens
• `AIAgent.config.radii` — Border radius tokens

### Templates
• `AIAgent.templates.page` — Full page template
• `AIAgent.templates.component` — Component template
• `AIAgent.templates.section` — Section template

### Usage
```javascript
// Generate a new page
const page = AIAgent.generate.page({
  name: 'about',
  title: 'About Us',
  description: 'Learn about our mission',
  content: '<section>...</section>'
});

// Generate SEO metadata
const seo = AIAgent.generate.seoMeta({
  title: 'About Us',
  description: 'Learn about our healing mission',
  url: '/about.html'
});

// Validate accessibility
const result = AIAgent.validate.accessibility(element);
```

